      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is my first blog post on this site, and I&amp;rsquo;m excited to start writing more regularly about the things I&amp;rsquo;m working on, reading about, or just thinking through.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hello and welcome.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;hello&#34;&gt;Hello&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Today, I wanted to test out a few things: Markdown formatting, section headings, and support for mathematical expressions using LaTeX. It’s important to have a workflow that lets me write comfortably without constantly switching contexts between writing and rendering.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
